methods.compact:
Compacts values into the front of the chunk, retaining only values where the parallel retainValues chunk has a
 true value.

:param values: (io.deephaven.chunk.WritableChunk<? extendsio.deephaven.chunk.attributes.Any>) - a chunk of values, input and output
:param retainValues: (io.deephaven.chunk.BooleanChunk<io.deephaven.chunk.attributes.Any>) - the values to retain
methods.compactAndCount:
**Incompatible overloads text - text from the first overload:**

For each run in valuesChunk, sort it, eliminate duplicates, and write the number of times a value occurred into
 the parallel slot within counts.

*Overload 1*  
  :param valueChunk: (io.deephaven.chunk.WritableChunk<? extendsio.deephaven.chunk.attributes.Values>) - a chunk of values, input and output
  :param counts: (io.deephaven.chunk.WritableIntChunk<io.deephaven.chunk.attributes.ChunkLengths>) - an output chunk parallel to valueChunk with the number of times a value occurred
  
*Overload 2*  
  :param valueChunk: (io.deephaven.chunk.WritableChunk<? extendsio.deephaven.chunk.attributes.Values>) - a chunk of values, input and output
  :param counts: (io.deephaven.chunk.WritableIntChunk<io.deephaven.chunk.attributes.ChunkLengths>) - an output chunk parallel to valueChunk with the number of times a value occurred
  :param countNull: (boolean) - if the compaction should count nulls or not
  
*Overload 3*  
  :param valueChunk: (io.deephaven.chunk.WritableChunk<? extendsio.deephaven.chunk.attributes.Values>) - a chunk of values, input and output
  :param counts: (io.deephaven.chunk.WritableIntChunk<io.deephaven.chunk.attributes.ChunkLengths>) - an output chunk parallel to valueChunk with the number of times a value occurred
  :param startPositions: (io.deephaven.chunk.IntChunk<io.deephaven.chunk.attributes.ChunkPositions>) - the start of each run
  :param lengths: (io.deephaven.chunk.WritableIntChunk<io.deephaven.chunk.attributes.ChunkLengths>) - the length of each run, input and output
  
*Overload 4*  
  :param valueChunk: (io.deephaven.chunk.WritableChunk<? extendsio.deephaven.chunk.attributes.Values>) - a chunk of values, input and output
  :param counts: (io.deephaven.chunk.WritableIntChunk<io.deephaven.chunk.attributes.ChunkLengths>) - an output chunk parallel to valueChunk with the number of times a value occurred
  :param startPositions: (io.deephaven.chunk.IntChunk<io.deephaven.chunk.attributes.ChunkPositions>) - the start of each run
  :param lengths: (io.deephaven.chunk.WritableIntChunk<io.deephaven.chunk.attributes.ChunkLengths>) - the length of each run, input and output
  :param countNull: (boolean) - if the compaction should count nulls or not
